{"tid":1520373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地以為大聲公襲警罪好荒謬一定告唔入？","createTime":"2019-08-30T18:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T14:06:27.000Z","uid":237123,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6045f28840da9e8ce1b1afa179819aa644b1eeff","tid":1520373,"uid":237123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T18:41:41.000Z","msg":"雖然係好荒謬 但居然有案例告得入<br />\n唔通係因為狗仔聽力係比人類敏感同脆弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用大聲公　襲警罪成<br />\n團體大遊行抗議警權過大<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2002-02-11</span><br />\n港 聞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】來自十多個團體的六十名人士昨日發起遊行，就社會福利員梁俊威被判入獄事件抗議警權過大；而與梁俊威拍拖三年的李小姐表示，考慮在初三情人節當天，託梁的家人將情人卡及禮物送到獄中，「雖然我哋𠵱家唔係喺埋一齊，但係我哋嘅心冇分開過！」礙於探監名額及次數限制，故當日她未能親身到監獄探望梁。 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">梁俊威因為於去年八月十一日與學聯就有關反對警方六二六胡椒噴霧報告的行動時在警員耳邊使用「大聲公」，被控襲警和阻差辦公罪，最後被裁定罪名成立，於上周四被判入獄五個月，即時執行。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n法律淪為鎮壓工具 <br />\n十多個團體包括學聯、支聯會、四五行動等昨日在遮打花園集合，遊行到灣仔警察總部請願，沿途高叫「警權無限大、人權被出賣、釋放梁俊威」等口號，抗議警方濫用法律鎮壓和平示威。 <br />\n示威人士抵達灣仔警察總部時，拒往側門的指定示威區，而直往正門大閘抗議，雙方擾攘十多分鐘後，警方讓步。 <br />\n示威者把一幅寫有「法律淪為警察鎮壓工具」的橫額掛在大閘上，又敲打鑼鼓等以增聲勢，並以廁紙筒及切除底部的膠水樽，諷刺警方禁用大聲公。<br />\n<br />\n「搞大大聲陪瞓營」 <br />\n發言人盧偉明表示，近期警方避開引用公安法控告示威人士，而以阻差辦公、阻街等提出檢控，並不公平。梁俊威的一些朋友更稱，將於每個周末、周日到監獄外「搞大大聲陪瞓營」來陪伴他。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20020211/2430218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20020211%2F2430218&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=d2d3cb7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20020211%2F2430218&h=973416c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20020211/2430218</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503c2e2cb006d7c59eaa9e5da5f0c3d1f69e942e","tid":1520373,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T18:41:49.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會 港島見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=1b9d58e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=729d0d4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=859de089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=d446b71c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293</a></span>"},{"pid":"de1b7f6c50512c5eb2